   <head>The Attestation of a friend touching this Booke, inserted in a Letter to <hi>the Translatour.</hi>
   </head>
   <p>—In your Translation you haue laboured, that they that will read may haue delight; and that they that are de<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>sirous to commit to memory might haue ease; and that all into whose hands it commeth might haue profit. 2 <hi>Ma<gap reason="illegible" resp="#keyers" extent="1 letter">
            <desc>•</desc>
         </gap>.</hi> 2.25</p>
   <closer>
      <signed>Adam Airay S.S. Theol. Bat.</signed>
   </closer>
